Package star.idres.lookup

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AISLookup
    An interface that defines methods for identifying the originating vessels of AIS messages.
    EnrichmentService
    Defines requests that perform the enrichment of position report messages.
    EnrichmentService.EnrichmentInfo
    The type that holds all the information that is needed to perform the enrichment of position messages for a given vessel.
    LRITLookup
    Defines methods to identify vessels transmitting LRIT messages.
    ReportingSystemLookup<T>
    A generic interface that defines the common methods used to retrieve the mapping between the transmitted identifiers and the surrogate identifiers.
    VMS.VMSID
    Type representing an identifier transmitted in a VMS message.
    VMSLookup
    Defines methods to identify senders of VMS messages.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VMS
    Utilities to deal with VMS data.
